fields.title: I ate a sandwich.
fields.content: everybody loves sanwiches, that's why everybody eats them. It's just stuff between bread.

fields.title: I'm healthy now.
fields.content: I don't eat sandwiches and candy all day like these dog-gone kids. It's attrocious what they're doing.

fields.title: I don't do anything anymore.
fields.content: I'm not bored. I'm mostly just sick of doing stuff. I have a great chair and I know every detail of the wall in front of me.
